## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Installation

# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Download Sub-JHMDB dataset to datasets/jhmdb_dataset/

# 3. Run the pipeline
python src/main_pipeline.py

# 4. Test on single image
python test_pipeline.py



